query:
UPDATE island_guides SET 
latitude = CASE slug
  WHEN 'thulusdhoo-island' THEN '4.374369'
  WHEN 'kandooma-island' THEN '3.90275'
  WHEN 'dhigurah-island' THEN '3.5225'
  WHEN 'rasdhoo-island' THEN '4.2628'
  WHEN 'veligandu-island' THEN '4.1667'
  WHEN 'maafushi-island' THEN '4.1833'
  WHEN 'fulidhoo-island' THEN '3.6333'
  WHEN 'felidhoo-island' THEN '3.5833'
  ELSE latitude
END,
longitude = CASE slug
  WHEN 'thulusdhoo-island' THEN '73.651413'
  WHEN 'kandooma-island' THEN '73.47362'
  WHEN 'dhigurah-island' THEN '72.9210'
  WHEN 'rasdhoo-island' THEN '72.9914'
  WHEN 'veligandu-island' THEN '72.8667'
  WHEN 'maafushi-island' THEN '72.8167'
  WHEN 'fulidhoo-island' THEN '72.8167'
  WHEN 'felidhoo-island' THEN '72.8500'
  ELSE longitude
END
WHERE slug IN ('thulusdhoo-island', 'kandooma-island', 'dhigurah-island', 'rasdhoo-island', 'veligandu-island', 'maafushi-island', 'fulidhoo-island', 'felidhoo-island');
